&quot;Yes, Sir!&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>The woman stood instantly at attention.  This was her first audience with Commander Bayle and she was on her best behaviour.<br>
<br>
As she watched the Commander pace before her rankmates and herself, she allowed herself a few moments to ponder where she'd be sent.<br>
<br>
The Bloodsabres picked a handful of promising youngsters every 10 years, to train for the Plaguebringer.  At the end of the rigorous training, Kane Bayle, himself, met with the survivors, to personally assess where they would best serve the Bloodsabres.<br>
<br>
This class boasted four graduates.  A young necromancer with no voice, who'd trained his minions to speak for him, a warrior, from the docks, smarmy and arrogant, but viscious and capable, an enchanter from one if Qeynos' more noble houses, and Asaviel, a knight whose memories start in the Plague Temple below Qeynos.<br>
<br>
As Commande Bayle finished his initial inspection, he stood before each recruit, to give them their assignments.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;And you, Asaviel...&quot; <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>The Commander smiled at her, impersonally, as he had to the other recruits.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
&quot;You must go to Luclin, Lady Knight.  There is much work to be done on that moon.  You will rent a room in Shadow Haven, and learn all that you can.  <br>
<br>
&quot;If you desire companionship, there is a guildhall there, run by a priestess and her mad husband. They are in need of the Plaguebringer's touch.   Cazic, Innoruuk, even the Warlord, and Solusek are represented in their ranks, but they boast no disease.<br>
<br>
&quot;So, go, and study Luclin, learn, and grow. Find new ways to bring pestilence, and serve Him.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>And with that, Asaviel was unleashed on the world, like one of the diseases she would soon bring.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bharvestersofdarkness.showUserPublicProfile?gid=silenaeonfirionavie>Silenae on FirionaVie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ambassador of the Scythe<br>
